---
title: Vegan Crispy Potato & Zucchini Tacos with Pico de Gallo, Cilantro Crema, and Tortilla Chips
description: What are taters doing in a taco, you ask? Everything, we say! Crispy roasted potatoes and zucchini are the perfect way to make taco night meatless (and just as satisfying). Load those deliciously spiced veggies into steamy flour tortillas, then enlist the help of some seriously satisfying toppings bring it all home: tangy pico de gallo, vegan cilantro crema, and hot sauce (plus tortilla chips on the side for crunch).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64b69f928c02aa034414111d-0d59a606.jpeg
